# affidavit-verify project ontology — deliberately empty of individuals.
#
# affidavit-pack's own ontology.ttl (packs/affidavit-pack/ontology.ttl) is a
# complete, closed model of both the CertifyStage pipeline individuals and
# (round 5) the DataStruct/DataField/ProfileIdVariant individuals; this
# consumer adds no project-specific facts on top of it (mirrors
# examples/praxis-core-verify/schema/domain.ttl's / examples/star-toml-verify
# /schema/domain.ttl's same posture). This file exists only to satisfy
# `[ontology] source` in ggen.toml — the real domain facts come entirely from
# the wired pack.

@prefix afd:  <http://seanchatmangpt.github.io/packs/affidavit#> .
@prefix rdf:  <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
